.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spearman%27s_rank_correlation_coefficient#cite_note-11"=
><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>11<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</spa=
n></a></sup> The confidence interval with level <span class=3D"mwe-math-ele=
ment mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-mat=
h-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/19=
98/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \alpha }">
