-align: -1.338ex; width:4.019ex; height:3.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \ch=
i _{1,\alpha }^{2}}"></span> is the <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-mat=
h-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11=
