racket">[</span>18<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D=
"cite_ref-Stephanou2020_19-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Spearman%27s_rank_correlation_coefficient#cite_note-Stephan=
ou2020-19"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>19<span class=3D"cite-brack=
et">]</span></a></sup> The first approach<sup id=3D"cite_ref-Xiao2019_18-1"=
 class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spearman%27s_=
rank_correlation_coefficient#cite_note-Xiao2019-18"><span class=3D"cite-bra=
