e>cor(x, y, method =3D "spearman")</code> will work). The package <a rel=3D=
"nofollow" class=3D"external text" href=3D"https://cran.r-project.org/web/p=
ackages/spearmanCI/index.html">spearmanCI</a> computes confidence intervals=
. The package <a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external text" href=3D"https://c=
