the <a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external text" href=3D"https://docs.scipy.=
org/doc/scipy/reference/generated/scipy.stats.spearmanr.html">spearmanr</a>=
 function of the <code>scipy.stats</code> module, as well as with the <code=
